    <title>Pycharm 远端同步设置（SSH Interpreter）</title>
    <url>/Python/pycharm-remote-synchronization-settings-ssh-interpreter.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="新建项目"><a href="#新建项目" class="headerlink" title="新建项目"></a>新建项目</h2><p><img src="http://mweb-tangjiuyang-com.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/2019/12/30/sshinterpreter1.png" alt="SSHInterpreter1"></p>
<a id="more"></a>

<h2 id="设置"><a href="#设置" class="headerlink" title="设置"></a>设置</h2><p>设置本地项目路径1，设置SSH编译器2，设置远端项目路径3（会自动与本地映射）<br><img src="http://mweb-tangjiuyang-com.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/2019/12/30/sshinterpreter2.png" alt="SSHInterpreter2"><br>interpreter 点击 “….”，选择<code>SSH interpreter</code><br><img src="http://mweb-tangjiuyang-com.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/2019/12/30/ssh4interpreter3.png" alt="SSHInterpreter3"><br><img src="http://mweb-tangjiuyang-com.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/2019/12/30/sshinterpreter4.png" alt="SSHInterpreter4"><br>最后设置一下 自动同步。<br><img src="http://mweb-tangjiuyang-com.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/2019/12/30/sshinterpreter5.png" alt="SSHInterpreter5"></p>
]]></content>
